# Copy to `.env` and adjust as needed. `.env` is gitignored and never committed.
#
# Which library profile the `ob` CLI and the MCP server use. Relative paths
# resolve against the repo root, so this works from any directory.
# Swap in another profile (e.g. profiles/diffusers.yaml) to re-theme every
# surface — CLI, Cursor rules, and MCP resources — with no code change.
OB_PROFILE=profiles/scikit-image.yaml
